@startuml
title Generate Report Cards Sequence Diagram
autonumber

actor "Homeroom Teacher" as Teacher
participant "Web Client" as UI
participant "Server Action" as Action
participant "Prisma ORM" as Prisma
database "Database" as DB

Teacher -> UI: Request Report Cards (Class)
activate UI
UI -> Action: generateReports(classId)
activate Action
Action -> Prisma: findMany({ include: { grades: true } })
activate Prisma
Prisma -> DB: SELECT Students & Grades...
activate DB
DB --> Prisma: Data
deactivate DB
Prisma --> Action: Data
deactivate Prisma

Action -> Action: Calculate GPA/Standings
activate Action
deactivate Action

Action --> UI: Report Data / PDF
deactivate Action
UI --> Teacher: Display/Download Reports
deactivate UI

@enduml
